\f1\b0\fs42 \cf0 Special equipment: an ice cream maker\
\
In a glass pitcher, combine the Mint Simple Syrup, pomegranate juice, and {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "http://www.foodterms.com/encyclopedia/orange/index.html"}}{\fldrslt \cf2 orange}} juice. Pour the pomegranate mixture in an {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "http://www.foodterms.com/encyclopedia/ice-cream/index.html"}}{\fldrslt \cf2 ice cream}} maker and freeze according to the manufacturer's instructions. During the last 10 minutes of freezing time, add the mini chocolate {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "http://www.foodterms.com/encyclopedia/chips/index.html"}}{\fldrslt \cf2 chips}}.\
\
Scoop the {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "http://www.foodterms.com/encyclopedia/sorbet/index.html"}}{\fldrslt \cf2 sorbet}} into dessert bowls and garnish with fresh mint sprigs.\
